title: Counter-Strike 1.6 | Find server patch | 2000 online Servers
description:
Can't find any servers on Counter-strike 1.6? - This patch will help you!

If you cant find servers on "find server" tab on Counter-Strike 1.6

When you got message like "Could not contact master game server to retrieve server list" or you get another problems with online servers. You just need to download this patch and install that to your Counter-Strike 1.6 game folder.

Enjoy


Installation

- Download
- Install to game folder
- Enjoying
